SbCTMRLEqMg.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/uBHZ7ItkIT11OubDkOVKYdLmv6F.jpg","iso_639_1":"tr","vote_average":0}]},"enriched_at":"2026-04-21T03:50:55.924+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"","runtime":112,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"A young man and woman from very different backgrounds fall in love but their relationship faces obstacles from his troubled past and her overprotective parents."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":110,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Bir barda çalışan Rüzgar, bir gün arkadaşına yardım etmek için onun yerine taksiye çıkar. Bu yolculukta hayatının aşkı Hayal ile tanışır. İkilisinin arasındaki aşk, Rüzgar'ın geçmişi ve Hayal'in ailesi sebebiyle bir çıkmaza girer."},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Film opowiada o Rüzgarze i Hayal, którzy mają zupełnie inne życie i kulturę, a także o ich przeszłości, która nigdy ich nie opuszcza, oraz o tym, jak trzymają się miłości."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":112,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Rüzgar arbeitet in einer Bar. Eines Tages bittet ihn sein Freund Ferit, sein Taxi zu fahren. Während dieser Fahrt lernt Rüzgar Hayal kennen, und sie verlieben sich ineinander. Doch als Hayals Familie von ihrer Beziehung erfährt, stellt sie sich vehement dagegen. Sie glauben, dass Rüzgar ein Mörder ist – doch die Wahrheit ist weitaus komplizierter. Rüzgars Vater tötete seine Mutter und schob ihm die Tat in die Schuhe..."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"الحب مجرد لحظة","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"العربية","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"SA","english_name":"Arabic"},{"data":{"title":"爱只在一瞬间","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Rüzgar和Hayal来自截然不同的世界。尽管他们有着截然不同的背景和文化障碍，但他们在坚持爱情的同时，驾驭着令人魂牵梦绕的过去。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"}],"reviews_tmdb":[],"recommendations":[{"id":1131759,"adult":false,"title":"Omniscient Reader: The Prophecy","video":false,"overview":"Kim Dok-ja, an ordinary man in his 20s, is the only reader of an obscure web novel titled \"Three Ways to Survive the Apocalypse\". After having read the last chapter, the novel suddenly becomes reality, and its omnipotent hero Yu Jung-hyeok appears before Kim. As the only person who knows how to survive in this world, Kim and his companions strive to save the world by writing his own, new ending.","genre_ids":[28,12,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":32.055,"vote_count":64,"poster_path":"/3R3dXO2nm8JyR5NG7SEfii7RzlV.jpg","release_date":"2025-07-23","vote_average":6.805,"backdrop_path":"/mZGsJUzQ4dONUBccxhImBqxaSQt.jpg","original_title":"전지적 독자 시점","original_language":"ko"},{"id":1339658,"adult":false,"title":"Oh, Hi!","video":false,"overview":"Iris and Isaac's first weekend away as a couple is going so well — until Isaac mentions he didn’t know they were a couple. Convinced she's met her perfect guy and that he's just confused, Iris goes to increasingly ridiculous and irrational lengths to prove to Isaac that they are meant to be together.","genre_ids":[10749,35,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":6.8094,"vote_count":130,"poster_path":"/8nBOFo78pKgzLipgGZhC8VA33wp.jpg","release_date":"2025-07-25","vote_average":6.35,"backdrop_path":"/1YeNl4OexgoTqCbwXEYg4ujZmYt.jpg","original_title":"Oh, Hi!","original_language":"en"},{"id":1402859,"adult":false,"title":"Quarantine","video":false,"overview":"Describing herself as a \"trouble magnet,\" Zeynep finds herself in the middle of chaos on her first day at her new school. An outbreak forces the school into lockdown, and that night, she stumbles upon the lifeless body of a female student in the dark hallways. She’s not alone—she’s joined by Onur Zorlu, the school principal’s son, and his friends Burak and Mert. Fearing his father’s weak heart won’t handle the news of a murder, Onur proposes they keep it a secret until the quarantine is lifted and find the killer themselves. With a disease outbreak and a murderer on the loose, the group believes their only option is to solve the mystery without alarming the parents outside. Drawn into this dangerous plan, Zeynep becomes the fourth, unexpected member of their group. Together, they embark on a perilous journey full of secrets, danger, and twists they never saw coming.","genre_ids":[18,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.6218,"vote_count":9,"poster_path":"/2BvjlOVoYqkJQD49mkD0MHGpxy.jpg","release_date":"2025-01-09","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":"/j1K0u3TQiCOM1mlxAjxAFyi2V77.jpg","original_title":"Karantina","original_language":"tr"},{"id":106646,"adult":false,"title":"The Wolf of Wall Street","video":false,"overview":"A New York stockbroker refuses to cooperate in a large securities fraud case involving corruption on Wall Street, corporate banking world and mob infiltration. Based on Jordan Belfort's autobiography.","genre_ids":[80,18,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":16.2479,"vote_count":25513,"poster_path":"/kW9LmvYHAaS9iA0tHmZVq8hQYoq.jpg","release_date":"2013-12-25","vote_average":8.026,"backdrop_path":"/7Nwnmyzrtd0FkcRyPqmdzTPppQa.jpg","original_title":"The Wolf of Wall Street","original_language":"en"},{"id":1278263,"adult":false,"title":"The Seed of the Sacred Fig","video":false,"overview":"Investigating judge Iman grapples with paranoia amid political unrest in Tehran. When his gun vanishes, he suspects his wife and daughters, imposing draconian measures that strain family ties as societal rules crumble.","genre_ids":[18,53,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.0066,"vote_count":425,"poster_path":"/ifOazNzv2cNJ5CQjMV7cPXG2Lmy.jpg","release_date":"2024-09-18","vote_average":7.559,"backdrop_path":"/zqZzYVE4DWv92xrYSCEELPcLnUP.jpg","original_title":"Les Graines du figuier sauvage","original_language":"fr"},{"id":666277,"adult":false,"title":"Past Lives","video":false,"overview":"After decades apart, childhood friends Nora and Hae Sung are reunited in New York for one fateful weekend as they confront notions of destiny, love, and the choices that make a life.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":6.7795,"vote_count":2198,"poster_path":"/k3waqVXSnvCZWfJYNtdamTgTtTA.jpg","release_date":"2023-06-02","vote_average":7.717,"backdrop_path":"/7HR38hMBl23lf38MAN63y4pKsHz.jpg","original_title":"Past Lives","original_language":"en"},{"id":1002155,"adult":false,"title":"Monsieur Aznavour","video":false,"overview":"From his poor childhood to his rise to fame, from his triumphs to his failures, from Paris to New York, discover the exceptional journey of an artist. Intimate, intense, fragile and indestructible, devoted to his art until the very end, here is one of the most immortal singers of all time: MONSIEUR AZNAVOUR.","genre_ids":[36,10402,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":4.0188,"vote_count":311,"poster_path":"/23FkaTaAosaTcTgyuJdTf7TvcJu.jpg","release_date":"2024-10-23","vote_average":7.198,"backdrop_path":"/1M9A2kW2jGCBEltdxrodXmujTEC.jpg","original_title":"Monsieur Aznavour","original_language":"fr"},{"id":551332,"adult":false,"title":"The Two Popes","video":false,"overview":"Frustrated with the direction of the church, Cardinal Bergoglio requests permission to retire in 2012 from Pope Benedict. Instead, facing scandal and self-doubt, the introspective Pope Benedict summons his harshest critic and future successor to Rome to reveal a secret that would shake the foundations of the Catholic Church.","genre_ids":[18,36],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.0392,"vote_count":3096,"poster_path":"/4d4mTSfDIFIbUbMLUfaKodvxYXA.jpg","release_date":"2019-11-27","vote_average":7.491,"backdrop_path":"/bOPessdyd0dChHy70FM8Om7CgDg.jpg","original_title":"The Two Popes","original_language":"en"},{"id":1151244,"adult":false,"title":"Vermiglio","video":false,"overview":"In the last days of the Second World War, a deserting soldier disrupts a tranquil and isolated mountain community. For one family, his arrival brings excitement and romance, but tragedy lies in wait.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.9587,"vote_count":302,"poster_path":"/aeCwM7c1Y1IAu3Oqqj5A2tSziWR.jpg","release_date":"2024-09-19","vote_average":7.061,"backdrop_path":"/fYepNPcgAYHQRMNZW95oOykLRgQ.jpg","original_title":"Vermiglio","original_language":"it"},{"id":517839,"adult":false,"title":"Border","video":false,"overview":"When a border guard with a sixth sense for identifying smugglers encounters the first person she cannot prove is guilty, she is forced to confront terrifying revelations about herself and humankind.","genre_ids":[14,18,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.7764,"vote_count":905,"poster_path":"/8KzOTRlKjdAKQTemV41hq86ldFS.jpg","release_date":"2018-09-27","vote_average":6.688,"backdrop_path":"/blHx3LrXsIfefFggOk4gjwdX73i.jpg","original_title":"Gräns","original_language":"sv"},{"id":8422,"adult":false,"title":"Rocco and His Brothers","video":false,"overview":"When a impoverished widow’s family moves to the big city, two of her five sons become romantic rivals with deadly results.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.0247,"vote_count":645,"poster_path":"/pngL8AraChIDOiWnKF2o3S9kJzJ.jpg","release_date":"1960-10-07","vote_average":7.993,"backdrop_path":"/zZCQs3tCkXLmZwArIsycQ5oby95.jpg","original_title":"Rocco e i suoi fratelli","original_language":"it"},{"id":1059128,"adult":false,"title":"Queer","video":false,"overview":"In 1950s Mexico City, William Lee, an American ex-pat in his late forties, leads a solitary life amidst a small American community. However, the arrival in town of Eugene Allerton, a young student, stirs William into finally establishing a meaningful connection with someone.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.1289,"vote_count":481,"poster_path":"/xe4b2TMciLKA1C0JlhWxb4ENLln.jpg","release_date":"2024-11-27","vote_average":6.6,"backdrop_path":"/7bUYzlDz8eel1BVL1Y0YcF9NQmd.jpg","original_title":"Queer","original_language":"en"},{"id":440298,"adult":false,"title":"Cold War","video":false,"overview":"A man and a woman meet in the ruins of post-war Poland. With vastly different backgrounds and temperaments, they are fatally mismatched and yet drawn to each other.","genre_ids":[10749,10402,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.7928,"vote_count":1560,"poster_path":"/6rbS8oPIgUMhQgIX8oGVTtlNgLR.jpg","release_date":"2018-06-08","vote_average":7.437,"backdrop_path":"/dXwXcBGK8LJ6UQVvuWM3qG6m6Co.jpg","original_title":"Zimna wojna","original_language":"pl"},{"id":475557,"adult":false,"title":"Joker","video":false,"overview":"During the 1980s, a failed stand-up comedian is driven insane and turns to a life of crime and chaos in Gotham City while becoming an infamous psychopathic crime figure.","genre_ids":[80,53,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":20.7457,"vote_count":27317,"poster_path":"/udDclJoHjfjb8Ekgsd4FDteOkCU.jpg","release_date":"2019-10-01","vote_average":8.128,"backdrop_path":"/hO7KbdvGOtDdeg0W4Y5nKEHeDDh.jpg","original_title":"Joker","original_language":"en"},{"id":1182047,"adult":false,"title":"The Apprentice","video":false,"overview":"A young Donald Trump, eager to make his name as a hungry scion of a wealthy family in 1970s New York, comes under the spell of Roy Cohn, the cutthroat attorney who would help create the Donald Trump we know today. Cohn sees in Trump the perfect protégé—someone with raw ambition, a hunger for success, and a willingness to do whatever it takes to win.","genre_ids":[36,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":4.1698,"vote_count":904,"poster_path":"/549Hdul2BgPnZMhqFxp6npp2opr.jpg","release_date":"2024-10-09","vote_average":6.864,"backdrop_path":"/kv9xVrxfLpudBLyYf1QvLCpUQuy.jpg","original_title":"The Apprentice","original_language":"en"},{"id":509364,"adult":false,"title":"By the Grace of God","video":false,"overview":"Alexandre, a man in his 40s living in Lyon with his wife and children, discovers that the priest who abused him decades ago continues to work with children. He joins forces with others victims of the priest, to bring justice and “lift the burden of silence” about what they endured.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.8006,"vote_count":582,"poster_path":"/qbwcnAdBkfGBIbQ1xdQZtiUg2lf.jpg","release_date":"2019-02-20","vote_average":7.1,"backdrop_path":"/86snn4qNnxfAbA5bXnvrHzhlXFI.jpg","original_title":"Grâce à Dieu","original_language":"fr"},{"id":273481,"adult":false,"title":"Sicario","video":false,"overview":"An idealistic FBI agent is enlisted by a government task force to aid in the escalating war against drugs at the border area between the U.S. and Mexico.","genre_ids":[28,80,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":8.7192,"vote_count":9335,"poster_path":"/lz8vNyXeidqqOdJW9ZjnDAMb5Vr.jpg","release_date":"2015-09-17","vote_average":7.416,"backdrop_path":"/meeileDF37uB8ykIs4iFb713ABO.jpg","original_title":"Sicario","original_language":"en"},{"id":398978,"adult":false,"title":"The Irishman","video":false,"overview":"Pennsylvania, 1956. Frank Sheeran, a war veteran of Irish origin who works as a truck driver, accidentally meets mobster Russell Bufalino. Once Frank becomes his trusted man, Bufalino sends him to Chicago with the task of helping Jimmy Hoffa, a powerful union leader related to organized crime, with whom Frank will maintain a close friendship for nearly twenty years.","genre_ids":[80,18,36],"media_type":"movie","popularity":8.3042,"vote_count":7349,"poster_path":"/mbm8k3GFhXS0ROd9AD1gqYbIFbM.jpg","release_date":"2019-11-01",