e":"en"},{"id":437265,"adult":false,"title":"Supesharu ressun: Hentai sei-kyôiku","video":false,"overview":"Lesbian-themed tale of a schoolgirl who entices her gullible (not to mention slightly warped) female teacher by positing that they are predestined to dance together on the day the world ends.","genre_ids":[18,27],"popularity":0.342,"vote_count":5,"poster_path":"/gpdAIQROkA0kbkLl5oy9FDHbDqv.jpg","release_date":"1990-09-01","vote_average":3.8,"backdrop_path":"/94QFqqP7BHedOZxKuLxJvmB56PV.jpg","original_title":"スペシャルレッスン 変態性教育","original_language":"ja"},{"id":2759,"adult":false,"title":"The Adventures of Priscilla, Queen of the Desert","video":false,"overview":"Two drag performers and a transgender woman travel across the desert to perform their unique style of cabaret.","genre_ids":[18,35],"popularity":3.4865,"vote_count":889,"poster_path":"/kJ7syYXEJgSBmBfSnF3Can9cK1J.jpg","release_date":"1994-05-31","vote_average":7.259,"backdrop_path":"/q1PuySDtRiKSgxAZjpIbFvvLOus.jpg","original_title":"The Adventures of Priscilla, Queen of the Desert","original_language":"en"},{"id":9388,"adult":false,"title":"Thank You for Smoking","video":false,"overview":"Nick Naylor is a charismatic spin-doctor for Big Tobacco who'll fight to protect America's right to smoke -- even if it kills him -- while still remaining a role model for his 12-year old son. When he incurs the wrath of a senator bent on snuffing out cigarettes, Nick's powers of \"filtering the truth\" will be put to the test.","genre_ids":[35,18],"popularity":2.2931,"vote_count":2349,"poster_path":"/41bMmglWT72OaRXrMROEyksOf3J.jpg","release_date":"2005-09-09","vote_average":7.189,"backdrop_path":"/qsBANxZSguLt5DD4lJa9DxXJjZL.jpg","original_title":"Thank You for Smoking","original_language":"en"},{"id":9410,"adult":false,"title":"Great Expectations","video":false,"overview":"Loosely based on the Charles Dickens' classic novel, \"Great Expectations\" is a sensual tale of a young man's unforgettable passage into manhood, and the three individuals who will undeniably change his life forever. Through the surprising interactions of these vivid characters, \"Great Expectations\" takes a unique and contemporary look at life's great coincidences.","genre_ids":[35,18,10749],"popularity":2.3374,"vote_count":665,"poster_path":"/djLsfl3lm7BZKWsKfVZ2wM1ZMrP.jpg","release_date":"1998-01-30","vote_average":6.623,"backdrop_path":"/laXkVCU5DE8Dib0QVHUUUsE7FM6.jpg","original_title":"Great Expectations","original_language":"en"},{"id":10802,"adult":false,"title":"Showgirls","video":false,"overview":"Fresh to Las Vegas with no connections, Nomi Malone takes a job as an exotic dancer. Her talents are quickly noticed by Cristal, a headlining dancer who senses an opportunity to bolster her own act. But Nomi won’t play second fiddle and soon begins her venomous path to the top, ruthlessly backstabbing anyone who gets in her way.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":6.6321,"vote_count":1350,"poster_path":"/o4HT3Ap5c99W4FYpdXUtTvxGgPc.jpg","release_date":"1995-09-22","vote_average":5.586,"backdrop_path":"/jL3G2f8uNCFejJRlIqCzRp8Y7eV.jpg","original_title":"Showgirls","original_language":"en"},{"id":9302,"adult":false,"title":"Up Close & Personal","video":false,"overview":"Tally Atwater has a dream: to be a prime-time network newscaster. She pursues this dream with nothing but ambition, raw talent and a homemade demo tape. Warren Justice is a brilliant, hard edged, veteran newsman. He sees Tally has talent and becomes her mentor. Tally’s career takes a meteoric rise and she and Warren fall in love. The romance that results is as intense and revealing as television news itself. Yet, each breaking story, every videotaped crisis that brings them together, also threatens to drive them apart...","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":0.955,"vote_count":234,"poster_path":"/zF67qcf7skMHLpXnifodinUqCFr.jpg","release_date":"1996-03-01","vote_average":6.278,"backdrop_path":"/wqD5zMFFITtzySK7fuYX42AtbJE.jpg","original_title":"Up Close & Personal","original_language":"en"},{"id":10400,"adult":false,"title":"The Hurricane","video":false,"overview":"The story of Rubin \"Hurricane\" Carter, a boxer wrongly imprisoned for murder, and the people who aided in his fight to prove his innocence.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":1.7474,"vote_count":1487,"poster_path":"/zhnxjsNnnpsBMF5V1H7Pzkec45Y.jpg","release_date":"1999-09-17","vote_average":7.4,"backdrop_path":"/ffAL7ZiUnCay51SeHFTrTEUpUkO.jpg","original_title":"The Hurricane","original_language":"en"},{"id":10243,"adult":false,"title":"The Flight of the Phoenix","video":false,"overview":"A cargo aircraft crashes in a sandstorm in the Sahara with less than a dozen men on board. One of the passengers is an airplane designer who comes up with the idea of ripping off the undamaged wing and using it as the basis for a replacement aircraft they need to build before their food and water run out.","genre_ids":[12,18],"popularity":1.6619,"vote_count":357,"poster_path":"/zrzLl7NWdjwGhVE7bqpOAxMVtF.jpg","release_date":"1965-12-15","vote_average":7.2,"backdrop_path":"/61cz8dZkyIo9m5bVwwfrYcvVZiK.jpg","original_title":"The Flight of the Phoenix","original_language":"en"},{"id":258654,"adult":false,"title":"Paradise for the Damned","video":false,"overview":"We all want to have a family. He is the only one willing to kill to get one","genre_ids":[18,53],"popularity":0.1129,"vote_count":5,"poster_path":"/uAxUy8jxLuThQEkyviIxfN62Ejq.jpg","release_date":"2013-11-07","vote_average":5,"backdrop_path":"/LaRE9Kjoqq05PU2OOWsMiXDj6T.jpg","original_title":"Un paraíso para los malditos","original_language":"es"},{"id":8489,"adult":false,"title":"Ali","video":false,"overview":"In 1964, a brash, new pro boxer, fresh from his Olympic gold medal victory, explodes onto the scene: Cassius Clay. Bold and outspoken, he cuts an entirely new image for African Americans in sport with his proud public self-confidence and his unapologetic belief that he is the greatest boxer of all time. Yet at the top of his game, both Ali's personal and professional lives face the ultimate test.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":3.1692,"vote_count":1830,"poster_path":"/3VIZRakftZZFys2ee9S7ufNNNyR.jpg","release_date":"2001-12-10","vote_average":6.753,"backdrop_path":"/bot4HZT2FWmq8IEcq7MhIVJSj1I.jpg","original_title":"Ali","original_language":"en"},{"id":9469,"adult":false,"title":"He Got Game","video":false,"overview":"A basketball player's father must try to convince him to go to a college so he can get a shorter prison sentence.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":1.8504,"vote_count":775,"poster_path":"/kd8hRaysUQOz7AvSorZDJHuihcJ.jpg","release_date":"1998-05-01","vote_average":6.8,"backdrop_path":"/zV1msPDVTn5B9KDAQNUnj8SKkX5.jpg","original_title":"He Got Game","original_language":"en"},{"id":599960,"adult":false,"title":"French Exit","video":false,"overview":"“My plan was to die before the money ran out,” says 60-year-old penniless Manhattan socialite Frances Price, but things didn’t go as planned. Her husband Franklin has been dead for 12 years and with his vast inheritance gone, she cashes in the last of her possessions and resolves to live out her twilight days anonymously in a borrowed apartment in Paris, accompanied by her directionless son Malcolm and a cat named Small Frank—who may or may not embody the spirit of Frances’s dead husband.","genre_ids":[35,18],"popularity":1.0477,"vote_count":166,"poster_path":"/l5iZuQr62YCs72AZ9P3HwApowaC.jpg","release_date":"2021-02-12","vote_average":5.639,"backdrop_path":"/4mDvrSNZuEc4OrbJdXnEJO8LLmO.jpg","original_title":"French Exit","original_language":"en"},{"id":11780,"adult":false,"title":"Rob Roy","video":false,"overview":"In the highlands of Scotland in the 1700s, Rob Roy tries to lead his small town to a better future, by borrowing money from the local nobility to buy cattle to herd to market. When the money is stolen, Rob is forced into a Robin Hood lifestyle to defend his family and honour.","genre_ids":[12,36,18,28,10752],"popularity":1.5265,"vote_count":695,"poster_path":"/kWI2rF6RAnRtEjfBlZgsXumgOm5.jpg","release_date":"1995-04-13","vote_average":6.703,"backdrop_path":"/yOwrZDFWdK2hjb4iOg8UEfNvNpJ.jpg","original_title":"Rob Roy","original_language":"en"},{"id":11866,"adult":false,"title":"Flight of the Phoenix","video":false,"overview":"When an oil rig in the Gobi Desert of Mongolia proves unproductive, an aircraft crew are sent to shut the operation down and fly them out. On the flight out over the desert on the way to Beijing, Capt. Frank Towns and co-pilot A.J. are unable to keep their cargo plane, a C-119 Flying Boxcar, in the air when a violent sandstorm strikes. Crash-landing in a remote uncharted part of the desert, the two pilots and their passengers -- a crew of oil workers and a drifter -- must work together to survive by rebuilding the aircraft. Soon, low supplies and a band of merciless smugglers add even greater urgency to their task.","genre_ids":[28,12,18],"popularity":2.2602,"vote_count":918,"poster_path":"/pcj6unMsKCw0ogWFlUXmbc9gKap.jpg","release_date":"2004-12-17","vote_average":6,"backdrop_path":"/mWXU29QjfjEG37d0c2hE11MWRGq.jpg","original_title":"Flight of the Phoenix","original_language":"en"},{"id":776490,"adult":false,"title":"The Pink Cloud","video":false,"overview":"After a toxic and mysterious pink cloud suddenly appears around the globe, people are forced to shelter in place. A woman finds herself stuck in an apartment with a stranger after a one-night stand, and the two come to terms with staying together.","genre_ids":[18,878],"popularity":0.146,"vote_count":39,"poster_path":"/5bLB5RnwXNxrXji49jcoxWopFnk.jpg","release_date":"2021-04-01","vote_average":5.756,"backdrop_path":"/yd9fYKqbsIXzyATqXKvsTxjEqEb.jpg","original_title":"A Nuvem Rosa","original_language":"pt"},{"id":10995,"adult":false,"title":"The Lover","video":false,"overview":"A poor French teenage girl engages in an illicit affair with a wealthy Chinese heir in 1920s Saigon. For the